### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Accept: application/json
X-API-Key: RAHASIA

### Create a new category
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: RAHASIA

{
  "name": "Computer"
}

